;; This repository's own entry in the loop-*/skill-*/action-* taxonomy
;; established by kotoba-lang/loop-ux-kaizen. Repeated here (not just
;; inherited by convention) so a reader of THIS repo alone can verify which
;; contract it claims to satisfy.
{:schema "kotoba.repository-role-rules.v0"
